title: Teyana Taylor Interview to What Are the Rules to 3 Somes?
itunes:title: Teyana Taylor Interview to What Are the Rules to 3 Somes?
description:
Friday 3/13 - Today on the show we had one of our favorite couples, Teyana Taylor and her husband Iman Shumpert stop by where they talked about her new album "KTSE", and threesomes, why not on this Freaky Friday. Moreover, when it comes to threesomes do you think certain rules apply? well we opened up the phone lines to see what our listeners thought. Also, Charalmagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a burglar that got stuck in Vancouver Escape Room, but panics and calls 911.
